WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:10.000
[English subtitles are available]

01:31.370 --> 01:34.920
[Road Home]

01:35.280 --> 01:37.780
[Episode 3]

01:46.090 --> 01:46.810
Lazybones.

01:46.850 --> 01:47.740
Get up. Hurry.

01:49.450 --> 01:50.920
I need to get some more sleep.

01:52.259 --> 01:53.500
Captain Lu's men are here.

02:01.090 --> 02:02.890
I haven't changed my clothes yet.

02:03.170 --> 02:04.130
Look how nervous you are.

02:04.130 --> 02:04.670
They're outside.

02:06.340 --> 02:07.550
Isn't the flight tomorrow?

02:07.870 --> 02:08.229
I just

02:08.259 --> 02:09.380
called him yesterday.

02:20.410 --> 02:21.370
Hello, Aunt Gui Xiao.

02:22.130 --> 02:22.890
Are you here alone?

02:24.250 --> 02:25.370
Uncle Lu is downstairs.

02:26.250 --> 02:27.680
Last night, Aunt Cai said

02:28.020 --> 02:28.950
she would take the train

02:28.970 --> 02:29.970
to go abroad for business today.

02:30.490 --> 02:31.970
My dad said he was off today.

02:32.760 --> 02:33.930
So he could send Aunt Cai off.

02:34.890 --> 02:36.410
Yes, I did mention it.

02:37.010 --> 02:37.770
Thank you so much.

02:38.460 --> 02:38.950
You're welcome.

02:48.079 --> 02:48.820
Good morning.

02:50.510 --> 02:51.010
Good morning.

02:51.240 --> 02:51.780
Morning, Captain Lu.

03:07.850 --> 03:08.650
Aunt Gui Xiao.

03:19.370 --> 03:19.710
Son.

03:29.079 --> 03:29.970
What time did you sleep last night?

03:32.210 --> 03:32.640
I didn't sleep.

03:33.570 --> 03:34.770
When we are on duty,

03:34.840 --> 03:36.570
it's normal not to sleep for a few days.

03:37.210 --> 03:37.800
I'm used to it already.

03:38.610 --> 03:40.090
It's not easy for the country to train you guys.

03:40.570 --> 03:41.450
You should take care of your health.

03:41.650 --> 03:42.940
So that you can work for a few more years.

04:00.320 --> 04:00.910
It's the border.

04:02.800 --> 04:04.780
Is the photo you sent to me

04:05.610 --> 04:06.230
taken here?

04:08.760 --> 04:09.180
No.

04:14.440 --> 04:14.960
Later on,

04:16.769 --> 04:17.920
if you come to Qining again,

04:19.050 --> 04:20.170
I'll ask them to take you

04:21.529 --> 04:22.430
to the place where the photo was taken.

04:26.100 --> 04:26.740
I don't know

04:26.800 --> 04:28.190
when will be the next time.

04:28.530 --> 04:29.530
The view here is nice.

04:30.470 --> 04:31.790
You should look more at

04:32.370 --> 04:33.090
the beautiful rivers and mountains of our motherland.

04:36.570 --> 04:38.090
You've lived here for more than ten years.

04:38.880 --> 04:39.470
I suppose

04:40.220 --> 04:41.970
it feels like looking at your hometown.

04:49.950 --> 04:57.680
[Qining Station]

05:07.890 --> 05:08.330
Captain Qin said

05:08.330 --> 05:09.690
he would help me watch over my car for a week

05:09.690 --> 05:10.350
until I returned.

05:10.610 --> 05:11.170
It's very nice of him.

05:14.250 --> 05:15.450
Captain Qin, thanks.

05:16.010 --> 05:16.930
Don't mention it. We're friends.

05:17.550 --> 05:17.990
Thank you.

05:20.800 --> 05:22.960
You may go through the customs and take the train from there.

05:24.610 --> 05:24.940
Captain Lu,

05:25.130 --> 05:26.050
once again, I would like to express

05:26.050 --> 05:26.890
my sincere gratitude to you.

05:27.570 --> 05:28.810
I'll treat you to a meal when I get back to Beijing.

05:29.970 --> 05:31.610
Captain Lu, see you again.

05:32.210 --> 05:32.530
Bye.

05:33.770 --> 05:34.900
Okay, you can go now.

05:35.010 --> 05:35.930
Take care.

05:36.490 --> 05:37.000
Have a safe trip.

05:37.250 --> 05:37.490
Okay.

05:37.520 --> 05:37.930
Bye.

05:44.350 --> 05:44.870
Aunt.

05:45.370 --> 05:46.159
Why don't you

05:46.159 --> 05:47.409
go abroad with them?

05:48.330 --> 05:49.490
I have work to do in Beijing.

05:49.510 --> 05:50.230
I need to go back to Beijing.

05:52.040 --> 05:53.560
The three of them came to Qining

05:53.830 --> 05:55.090
for foreign trade.

05:55.890 --> 05:57.409
Aunt, why are you here?

06:00.370 --> 06:02.450
Are you coming specially for Uncle Lu?

06:04.130 --> 06:04.820
No.

06:05.210 --> 06:05.770
How could it be?

06:08.850 --> 06:10.610
Xiaonan, if you keep talking nonsense,

06:10.610 --> 06:11.610
Aunt won't take you with her anymore.

06:18.550 --> 06:18.900
Lu.

06:19.810 --> 06:20.370
I've got an emergency mission.

06:21.410 --> 06:22.140
I'll leave them to you.

06:22.590 --> 06:22.950
Go ahead.

06:24.530 --> 06:26.050
Xiaonan, be obedient to Aunt.

06:29.530 --> 06:29.930
Thank you.

06:34.470 --> 06:36.570
Aunt, are you free after this?

06:37.000 --> 06:37.490
Yes, I am.

06:38.210 --> 06:40.210
Can you help me pack up my luggage?

06:41.810 --> 06:43.010
Why can't you do it yourself?

06:45.330 --> 06:45.970
What do you

06:45.970 --> 06:47.090
need help with from others?

06:48.080 --> 06:49.280
None of us can.

06:50.010 --> 06:51.010
Men are not careful enough.

06:51.610 --> 06:52.760
We'll leave something out.

06:56.690 --> 06:57.070
Okay.

06:57.930 --> 06:58.280
Thank you.

07:14.970 --> 07:16.920
Does he live alone?

07:19.810 --> 07:20.650
When his dad comes,

07:21.250 --> 07:22.410
he makes the bed up there

07:22.970 --> 07:23.530
and sleeps on the upper bunk.

07:24.410 --> 07:25.810
Why doesn't he apply for a dorm,

07:25.810 --> 07:26.650
taking his son together?

07:29.460 --> 07:30.420
In our profession,

07:31.530 --> 07:32.530
once there is a mission,

07:33.170 --> 07:34.050
our working hours will be uncertain.

07:35.530 --> 07:36.770
If the kid stays in the dorm,

07:37.510 --> 07:38.480
first, his resting will be disturbed.

07:39.270 --> 07:40.590
Second, seeing his dad often goes out,

07:41.080 --> 07:41.770
he'll be worried.

07:44.780 --> 07:46.090
Kids nowadays are smart.

07:47.010 --> 07:48.450
He knows his dad's profession.

07:48.850 --> 07:49.850
He'll be worried anyway.

07:51.180 --> 07:51.770
Besides,

07:51.770 --> 07:53.480
there're numerous movies about explosive ordnance disposal nowadays.

07:53.480 --> 07:54.090
Doesn't he

07:54.090 --> 07:55.450
ask you guys after watching them?

07:56.000 --> 07:57.409
Usually, we would say that

07:58.000 --> 07:59.070
the movie scenes are all made-up.

07:59.850 --> 08:00.570
It's not that dangerous.

08:03.460 --> 08:04.500
So it's all true.

08:06.410 --> 08:07.450
It's dangerous, isn't it?

08:13.340 --> 08:14.420
Can't you even tell your friends?

08:17.850 --> 08:19.050
Every profession has difficulty.

08:19.890 --> 08:20.650
There's nothing to say.

08:34.010 --> 08:34.650
Is this all?

08:39.130 --> 08:39.470
Doesn't his father

08:39.510 --> 08:41.059
buy him clothes?

08:42.210 --> 08:43.289
Also, why doesn't

08:43.289 --> 08:43.929
he rent

08:43.929 --> 08:44.890
a more spacious house?

08:46.370 --> 08:47.370
Isn't it too small

08:47.370 --> 08:48.730
for them to live here?

09:02.370 --> 09:03.060
Are they your parents?

09:05.360 --> 09:07.030
It's Uncle Lu and...

09:07.810 --> 09:10.910
Maybe

09:11.270 --> 09:12.330
his alumnus.

09:12.880 --> 09:13.970
Why can't I understand

09:15.170 --> 09:16.450
what you said?

09:19.530 --> 09:20.080
Captain Lu is here.

09:20.280 --> 09:20.950
I have to say hello to him.

09:22.410 --> 09:23.930
They're developing feelings for each other.

09:28.530 --> 09:29.750
Are they helping you pack

09:30.080 --> 09:30.740
and move?

09:32.660 --> 09:33.450
Thank you

09:34.190 --> 09:35.370
for taking care of me all this time.

09:37.240 --> 09:38.150
Why did you close the door?

09:38.520 --> 09:40.330
The kid outside will get it wrong.

09:42.090 --> 09:42.930
We can talk conveniently if the door is closed.

09:48.290 --> 09:49.050
His parents are divorced.

09:50.170 --> 09:51.490
Qin Mingyu got his son.

09:52.550 --> 09:53.720
But deep down,

09:54.470 --> 09:55.490
he felt that he had dragged on Xiaonan's mother,

09:56.250 --> 09:57.350
so he paid her a lot of money.

10:00.690 --> 10:01.170
I see.

10:05.180 --> 10:06.270
Now he has to take care of his parents

10:06.640 --> 10:07.400
and raise his son.

10:08.450 --> 10:09.210
So he doesn't dare to spend money freely.

10:15.330 --> 10:16.490
I've done packing the clothes.

10:17.290 --> 10:19.150
I'll leave the books for you to pack since you're more familiar with them.

10:19.530 --> 10:20.330
I'll go out first.

10:23.030 --> 10:25.940
♫We said it would last forever♫

10:25.970 --> 10:27.580
♫But we were separated in the end♫

10:27.880 --> 10:30.090
♫I wait until I give up all resistance♫

10:30.110 --> 10:31.840
♫Let time pass by♫

10:31.920 --> 10:33.300
♫Never thought that love♫

10:33.320 --> 10:35.920
♫Is not about the trials and tribulations♫

10:36.210 --> 10:36.770
My dad said...

10:40.050 --> 10:42.170
My dad said that

10:42.550 --> 10:43.560
he was not coming back for dinner tonight.

10:43.890 --> 10:44.310
I got it.

10:47.410 --> 10:47.960
Let me see.

10:48.370 --> 10:49.110
It's okay.

10:49.370 --> 10:50.210
I'll go out first.

10:50.210 --> 10:51.250
Otherwise, the kid will misunderstand.

10:52.410 --> 10:52.850
Get out.

10:59.090 --> 11:00.450
This is even more misunderstanding.

11:13.810 --> 11:14.320
Remember to take

11:14.320 --> 11:15.330
Qin Xiaonan's household registration permit

11:15.400 --> 11:15.950
for boarding purposes.

11:20.570 --> 11:21.290
Stay in the car.

11:21.870 --> 11:22.780
I need to talk to your aunt.

11:41.060 --> 11:41.900
He doesn't have a household registration permit.

11:42.610 --> 11:43.250
He doesn't?

11:45.290 --> 11:45.840
His household registration permit

11:45.840 --> 11:46.730
has been with his mother.

11:47.470 --> 11:48.290
After the divorce,

11:48.330 --> 11:49.120
his mother always hopes

11:49.150 --> 11:50.090
Xiaonan can live with her.

11:50.960 --> 11:52.040
Although the court has made a judgment,

11:52.810 --> 11:53.580
these two

11:53.910 --> 11:55.270
have been dilly-dallying regarding household registration.

11:56.130 --> 11:56.950
Qin Mingyu is also busy

11:57.450 --> 11:58.440
that he has no time to do it.

11:59.450 --> 12:00.330
Then, what should we do?

12:04.770 --> 12:05.520
Does he have a passport?

12:06.000 --> 12:06.470
Yes.

12:07.900 --> 12:08.910
Give me his passport first.

12:09.370 --> 12:10.350
We'll discuss it after flying to Beijing.

12:11.050 --> 12:11.850
But we need

12:11.850 --> 12:12.850
both the original and photocopy

12:12.850 --> 12:13.540
of his household registration permit.

12:13.930 --> 12:14.730
The school will need to verify them.

12:16.980 --> 12:18.130
We'll figure this out this month.

12:24.970 --> 12:27.290
Poor kid.

12:33.620 --> 12:36.570
[No self-heating food in hand-carry or check-in luggage is allowed]

12:45.010 --> 12:45.450
Passport.

13:09.890 --> 13:11.540
I'll go back to Beijing after the Chinese New Year.

13:16.930 --> 13:17.610
It's almost time.

13:18.450 --> 13:18.900
You may go in.

13:22.970 --> 13:24.010
Goodbye, Uncle Lu.

13:24.970 --> 13:25.420
Alright.

13:26.170 --> 13:26.880
It's not like we'll never see each other again.

13:29.010 --> 13:29.770
We'll get going then.

14:27.120 --> 14:28.710
Why didn't your dad come to see you off?

14:30.490 --> 14:32.810
He hasn't been home for two days.

14:35.730 --> 14:36.930
He only called once.

14:39.850 --> 14:40.410
It's okay.

14:41.210 --> 14:42.450
You can visit him during the summer break.

14:43.310 --> 14:44.110
I may not able to see him

14:45.800 --> 14:47.120
even if I go back.

14:49.590 --> 14:51.630
Last year when I just arrived at Qining,

14:52.840 --> 14:54.360
my dad was on a mission,

14:55.690 --> 14:56.170
a confidential one.

14:57.980 --> 14:59.330
I couldn't see him for days.

15:02.480 --> 15:02.970
Then,

15:04.090 --> 15:04.900
what about you?

15:05.130 --> 15:05.970
Was there no one who took care of you?

15:06.890 --> 15:07.450
Yes.

15:08.620 --> 15:10.700
The family of other team members took turns taking care of me.

15:12.000 --> 15:14.670
But I cried every night.

15:15.600 --> 15:18.360
I thought my dad had abandoned me.

15:22.050 --> 15:22.810
Let me tell you.

15:23.730 --> 15:26.850
I even cried

15:26.850 --> 15:27.770
when I was in high school.

15:28.410 --> 15:29.730
My parents were divorcing at that time.

15:30.410 --> 15:31.090
So I cried a lot.

15:31.770 --> 15:32.770
You are so melodramatic.

15:35.880 --> 15:37.650
What's wrong with you?

15:37.650 --> 15:39.170
I was trying to comfort you.

15:41.420 --> 15:43.140
My dad said that I couldn't lie,

15:43.770 --> 15:44.680
especially to you.

15:46.870 --> 15:48.240
So I was being honest with you.

15:50.650 --> 15:51.410
I won't argue with you.

15:55.080 --> 15:56.300
I'll take you hanging out tomorrow.

15:56.870 --> 15:57.470
Where do you want to go?

15:58.030 --> 15:59.680
The Palace Museum, the Temple of Heaven

16:00.170 --> 16:01.210
or the Great Wall?

16:02.490 --> 16:03.010
How about this?

16:03.450 --> 16:03.930
I'll take you

16:03.960 --> 16:05.130
to visit

16:05.130 --> 16:05.890
all the famous tourist spots

16:06.560 --> 16:08.170
before we go to the local spots.

16:09.580 --> 16:10.590
I don't want to go anywhere.

16:12.180 --> 16:13.580
We don't spend your dad's money.

16:14.600 --> 16:16.890
Your money is also money.

16:23.360 --> 16:24.410
That's Xinhe Hospital.

16:27.120 --> 16:27.890
Do you know it?

16:29.610 --> 16:30.150
I know.

16:31.220 --> 16:32.580
I used to go there when I was young.

16:33.430 --> 16:34.820
And there's also a 341 Hospital.

16:35.200 --> 16:36.770
Is it nearby?

16:38.490 --> 16:39.170
I know it too.

16:40.100 --> 16:41.430
You know a lot.

16:43.250 --> 16:44.250
Uncle Lu told me.

16:45.450 --> 16:46.370
He said

16:46.460 --> 16:47.840
he went to 341 Hospital

16:49.840 --> 16:51.030
to visit a friend.

16:53.190 --> 16:53.990
A hospitalized friend.

16:55.490 --> 16:56.330
Is it you?

17:02.690 --> 17:03.560
Maybe.

17:04.410 --> 17:07.430
What do you mean by maybe?

17:09.250 --> 17:10.810
I can't remember.

17:15.849 --> 17:16.810
We are arriving at my home.

17:17.420 --> 17:18.609
That is the place you are going to stay

17:18.650 --> 17:19.450
for the next month.

17:36.410 --> 17:36.720
Come in.

17:42.210 --> 17:43.370
This is the house I rent.

17:43.530 --> 17:44.410
You can look around later.

17:47.440 --> 17:48.050
Come and change your shoes.

17:51.880 --> 17:52.630
Put them on.

18:02.480 --> 18:03.790
I can't help you manage the suitcase today.

18:04.570 --> 18:05.730
Take out your pyjamas.

18:05.730 --> 18:06.890
I'll take you upstairs to take a shower and go to bed.

18:12.900 --> 18:15.150
I usually

18:16.690 --> 18:17.290
sleep naked.

18:19.120 --> 18:20.530
You have to wear clothes here.

18:20.930 --> 18:21.730
I'm a girl.

18:22.050 --> 18:23.230
We should respect each other.

18:24.890 --> 18:25.410
Okay.

18:52.130 --> 18:53.250
I'm not familiar with this place.

18:54.250 --> 18:56.700
Can you buy it for me tomorrow?

19:00.210 --> 19:01.740
Okay, leave it to me.

19:08.950 --> 19:12.260
[Hongrun Chenghua]

19:14.970 --> 19:15.490
Thanks.

19:17.490 --> 19:18.690
You finally came back.

19:19.130 --> 19:20.170
Didn't you be tied

19:20.170 --> 19:20.890
by the beautiful mountains and rivers of our motherland?

19:23.530 --> 19:24.410
Did anything happen

19:24.410 --> 19:25.330
before the Chinese New Year?

19:26.140 --> 19:26.820
No.

19:26.920 --> 19:28.390
It's almost New Year. Everyone is lazy.

19:29.080 --> 19:29.690
That's good.

19:30.330 --> 19:30.690
By the way,

19:31.060 --> 19:32.230
there's a kid at my house.

19:32.520 --> 19:33.690
He's the child of my friend.

19:33.770 --> 19:35.250
So I won't work overtime.

19:35.530 --> 19:36.290
If there are any needs,

19:36.290 --> 19:37.110
I'll work from home.

19:38.020 --> 19:39.020
I'm fine with it.

19:39.250 --> 19:39.990
I'm not the boss.

19:43.950 --> 19:44.970
The boss is coming.

19:46.540 --> 19:46.990
You're back.

19:49.690 --> 19:50.370
Tomorrow is Laba.

19:50.890 --> 19:51.930
I was worried

19:51.930 --> 19:53.530
you wouldn't be able to catch up with the congee from Yonghe Palace.

19:53.890 --> 19:54.250
Perfect.

19:55.130 --> 19:55.820
Oh yeah.

19:55.850 --> 19:56.970
I almost forgot.

19:59.720 --> 20:01.530
Are we going together tomorrow

20:01.550 --> 20:02.760
or I queue up for you first?

20:03.090 --> 20:03.690
No need.

20:03.910 --> 20:04.750
I'll take someone there.

20:08.450 --> 20:09.540
Her friend's kid

20:09.600 --> 20:10.750
will stay at her house until the Chinese New Year.

20:12.770 --> 20:13.200
Okay.

20:24.400 --> 20:25.130
Qin Xiaonan.

20:26.040 --> 20:26.710
-Qin...
-Coming.

20:28.190 --> 20:30.050
Slow down. Be careful not to fall.

20:30.770 --> 20:31.950
You've underestimated me.

20:32.430 --> 20:33.310
These stairs

20:33.730 --> 20:34.490
won't hurt me.

20:35.500 --> 20:36.780
Why didn't you turn on the lights?

20:36.890 --> 20:37.890
It was dark when I came in.

20:37.890 --> 20:38.490
You scared me.

20:38.490 --> 20:39.730
I thought something happened to you.

20:40.130 --> 20:40.750
It's on.

20:41.610 --> 20:42.730
I've turned on the desk lamp.

20:43.600 --> 20:45.120
Your lights are too bright.

20:45.560 --> 20:46.290
It must consume a lot of electricity.

20:47.180 --> 20:48.440
I was not in the living room.

20:48.670 --> 20:50.340
so I switched off all of them.

20:53.090 --> 20:53.450
Come here.

20:55.300 --> 20:57.260
Women like shopping.

20:58.370 --> 20:59.770
These are all for you.

20:59.770 --> 21:00.680
Heartless boy.

21:02.540 --> 21:04.260
I don't have that much money for you.

21:07.410 --> 21:09.770
They are at a 90% discount.

21:09.810 --> 21:10.850
All are on sale.

21:11.370 --> 21:12.330
I spent all the money

21:12.330 --> 21:13.770
you gave me to buy these.

21:15.090 --> 21:16.540
And I have points

21:16.640 --> 21:17.730
to redeem the gifts for free.

21:19.130 --> 21:20.010
Points?

21:20.930 --> 21:22.370
You can redeem so many things?

21:22.490 --> 21:23.270
Of course.

21:23.770 --> 21:24.730
I bought a lot in the past.

21:24.730 --> 21:25.940
So I got many points.

21:26.410 --> 21:27.260
You lied to me.

21:30.290 --> 21:31.230
You money-grubber.

21:31.380 --> 21:32.950
You still have your wallet with you.

21:34.330 --> 21:35.170
What do you want for dinner?

21:35.170 --> 21:35.810
I'll order takeout.

21:43.060 --> 21:46.890
[Qining City]

21:55.520 --> 21:56.570
You are leaving one week earlier

21:56.600 --> 21:57.600
than planned.

21:57.810 --> 21:58.730
Are you anxious to return home?

21:59.850 --> 22:00.850
Your son is in Beijing.

22:01.400 --> 22:02.090
Aren't you worried?

22:03.570 --> 22:04.690
He is with Gui Xiao.

22:05.050 --> 22:05.930
It's better than with you.

22:18.250 --> 22:18.770
Give this to Gui Xiao.

22:19.490 --> 22:20.210
It's for Xiaonan's living expenses.

22:22.050 --> 22:22.800
Where did you get the money?

22:23.150 --> 22:23.670
It's my bonus.

22:28.490 --> 22:29.730
Gui Xiao bought not only clothes

22:29.750 --> 22:31.280
but also books for Xiaonan.

22:31.490 --> 22:32.730
Right? She provides food and accommodation.

22:32.730 --> 22:33.810
We can't pretend to be unaware of it.

22:34.330 --> 22:34.890
Also,

22:35.490 --> 22:36.170
most importantly,

22:36.170 --> 22:37.570
she introduced me to a school.

22:38.300 --> 22:38.970
A school?

22:39.570 --> 22:40.610
This helped me a lot.

22:40.610 --> 22:41.690
She has done me a huge favour.

22:41.690 --> 22:43.040
Favour is the most valuable, do you know that?

22:43.410 --> 22:43.770
Take it.

22:44.880 --> 22:45.360
I will pay her.

22:46.910 --> 22:48.670
You should keep your bonus to celebrate the New Year with your family.

22:49.910 --> 22:50.850
What do you mean

22:50.850 --> 22:51.650
by paying for my son?

22:53.290 --> 22:53.890
It's on your account.

22:54.490 --> 22:55.450
When you become rich,

22:56.170 --> 22:56.650
pay me triple.

22:58.370 --> 22:58.740
Okay.

23:09.050 --> 23:09.530
Captain Lu.

23:11.730 --> 23:12.650
I might come back in the future.

23:13.540 --> 23:14.700
You'd better not come back.

23:15.290 --> 23:17.090
It's not easy for you to transfer back there.

23:17.090 --> 23:17.950
You should make up with

23:17.970 --> 23:18.600
our ex-sister-in-law.

23:19.730 --> 23:20.730
You're over 30 years old

23:20.730 --> 23:21.650
but you still care about your pride.

23:21.650 --> 23:22.930
If you like her, just go for it.

23:23.050 --> 23:23.570
Shut up.

23:24.810 --> 23:25.210
I'm leaving.

23:30.050 --> 23:30.690
Take a leave as soon as possible

23:31.300 --> 23:32.280
and get the household registration permit back.

23:32.510 --> 23:32.990
I remember that.

24:23.420 --> 24:25.700
[Beijing City]

24:26.600 --> 24:28.710
[Outside the Fifth Ring]

24:47.260 --> 24:48.490
You're finally back.

24:48.490 --> 24:49.250
Why didn't you inform me?

24:49.250 --> 24:50.290
I would pick you up.

24:51.490 --> 24:52.090
Let me see.

24:53.970 --> 24:55.020
The campus beau in those days

24:55.170 --> 24:56.210
is still so handsome.

24:56.210 --> 24:56.770
Screw you!

24:57.290 --> 24:57.730
Let's go.

24:58.330 --> 24:58.650
Go home.

25:00.650 --> 25:01.650
I've booked

25:01.650 --> 25:02.970
the fanciest restaurant next to our house

25:03.010 --> 25:04.100
to welcome you.

25:04.420 --> 25:05.480
I don't have time to eat with you.

25:06.360 --> 25:06.990
My mum is sick.

25:07.690 --> 25:08.090
I came back

25:08.090 --> 25:09.170
to pack a change of clothes

25:09.170 --> 25:09.910
before I go to the hospital.

25:11.310 --> 25:12.260
Your mum is sick?

25:14.250 --> 25:15.330
It's my fault.

25:15.330 --> 25:15.970
I've been doing business

25:15.970 --> 25:17.310
outside.

25:17.510 --> 25:19.140
So I haven't had a chance to visit your mum.

25:25.810 --> 25:26.430
Meng Xiaoshan.

25:27.020 --> 25:27.900
Cancel the table

25:27.920 --> 25:28.720
I reserved for tonight.

25:29.690 --> 25:30.730
I'm not going.

25:32.180 --> 25:32.930
My younger brother

25:32.930 --> 25:33.930
is dealing with the school application for Xiaonan.

25:34.620 --> 25:36.010
Have you got his household registration permit

25:36.010 --> 25:36.690
and birth certificate?

25:37.990 --> 25:38.720
Don't worry.

25:38.740 --> 25:39.750
I'll be there next time.

25:40.490 --> 25:41.010
Don't worry.

25:44.510 --> 25:45.210
I haven't got them yet.

25:45.730 --> 25:47.100
Sorry, I'll be quick.

25:49.610 --> 25:50.080
Not yet.

25:51.540 --> 25:52.240
Let's make up for it later.

25:52.500 --> 25:53.340
Since it's confirmed,

25:53.600 --> 25:54.780
I'll hold off for you with my guarantee.

25:56.090 --> 25:56.520
Thanks.

25:57.360 --> 25:58.030
What's wrong with you?

25:59.690 --> 26:00.210
How many donations

26:00.210 --> 26:01.370
has Sister made for us

26:01.370 --> 26:02.010
for the mountainous area?

26:02.770 --> 26:03.470
Without her,

26:03.490 --> 26:04.790
would you have connected with so many prestigious schools?

26:06.010 --> 26:07.090
Guarantee?

26:07.480 --> 26:08.680
Your guarantee is valid because of Sister.

26:08.720 --> 26:09.360
Yes.

26:10.240 --> 26:10.880
Don't bother him, Sister.

26:11.850 --> 26:12.450
Well,

26:12.490 --> 26:13.770
as for the procedures afterwards,

26:13.770 --> 26:15.370
make a list for me.

26:15.540 --> 26:16.590
I'll finish them during the winter break.

26:16.780 --> 26:17.330
I'll give it to you tomorrow.

26:17.330 --> 26:17.730
Okay.

26:21.010 --> 26:22.010
I'll get it for you, Uncle.

26:22.950 --> 26:23.640
Good boy.

26:28.130 --> 26:29.530
You've been to the north

26:30.370 --> 26:31.290
for less than a week,

26:31.290 --> 26:31.850
but you took back

26:31.850 --> 26:32.810
a kid you didn't know before.

26:33.230 --> 26:33.870
Not only are you

26:33.910 --> 26:34.990
helping with his education,

26:35.200 --> 26:36.690
but you also filled in his regular address as your home.

26:37.170 --> 26:38.610
Sister, if you weren't a woman

26:38.700 --> 26:40.050
and couldn't satisfy the condition,

26:40.050 --> 26:40.930
I would have thought that

26:40.930 --> 26:41.560
he was

26:41.590 --> 26:42.230
your illegitimate child.

26:42.850 --> 26:43.970
You're right.

26:43.970 --> 26:44.370
Right?

26:48.250 --> 26:49.290
Let's have dinner together tonight.

26:49.320 --> 26:50.040
I'll book a restaurant.

26:50.670 --> 26:52.040
Don't bother, Sister. You're always so generous.

26:52.850 --> 26:54.210
Can't I take the kid

26:54.210 --> 26:54.770
to have some meat?

26:56.340 --> 26:57.570
Go. Put on your down jacket.

26:57.840 --> 26:58.740
The one I bought for you.

27:00.650 --> 27:01.130
How about this?

27:01.320 --> 27:02.210
We'll go downstairs and wait in the car.

27:02.310 --> 27:03.480
Okay, see you downstairs.

27:14.780 --> 27:15.170
Take it.

27:23.860 --> 27:24.780
Okay, let's go.

27:25.620 --> 27:28.660
[Inpatient Building]

27:35.170 --> 27:35.740
Here's your bill.

27:35.970 --> 27:36.370
Okay.

27:41.490 --> 27:42.690
Do you have enough money? I have some with me.

27:43.330 --> 27:43.730
Yes.

27:52.610 --> 27:53.020
It's settled.

27:56.180 --> 27:57.790
It's not like you to smile at your phone.

27:58.700 --> 27:59.450
Is it a beauty from Qining?

28:01.930 --> 28:02.890
Watch over my mum.

28:02.910 --> 28:03.430
I'll pay the bill.

28:14.600 --> 28:15.440
My dad said

28:16.010 --> 28:17.720
Uncle Lu always risked his life on missions.

28:18.580 --> 28:19.420
He led the team to arrest the culprits

28:20.780 --> 28:22.040
for two days and two nights.

28:22.850 --> 28:24.170
After crossing five snow-capped mountains,

28:24.830 --> 28:27.410
the claws of police dogs covered with blood,

28:28.260 --> 28:29.040
he was still chasing after them.

28:42.440 --> 28:43.290
In the end, he caught them.

28:45.170 --> 28:46.240
Nobody can get away

28:46.240 --> 28:47.250
from Uncle Lu.

28:50.130 --> 28:51.810
Once, they went on a mission

28:53.250 --> 28:54.890
at a forbidden zone of life

28:54.910 --> 28:55.750
with an elevation of about 5,000 metres.

28:56.420 --> 28:57.890
They'd walked a dozen kilometres

28:58.840 --> 29:02.080
and carried out the villagers who passed out with oxygen deficiency.

29:03.150 --> 29:04.390
The villagers recovered after being carried out,

29:05.390 --> 29:06.730
but some team members had altitude sickness

29:07.160 --> 29:08.200
and almost died.

29:47.000 --> 29:47.800
Aunt Gui Xiao.

29:49.130 --> 29:49.930
How did you

29:50.890 --> 29:51.730
know each other?

29:54.600 --> 29:55.090
We're alumni.

29:55.630 --> 29:56.670
You're indeed alumni?

29:58.530 --> 30:00.360
I thought it was an excuse.

30:01.340 --> 30:02.820
His name was Lu Chen at first.

30:03.410 --> 30:05.160
Later, he changed his name by adding Yan in the middle.

30:05.930 --> 30:06.370
Do you know that?

30:08.890 --> 30:09.810
No wonder.

30:10.850 --> 30:11.610
No wonder what?

30:12.170 --> 30:14.250
That day in the parking lot,

30:15.090 --> 30:16.290
you called him Lu Chen.

30:17.490 --> 30:18.720
I felt weird at that time.

30:22.970 --> 30:24.080
Although we went to the same school,

30:25.200 --> 30:25.890
I hadn't met him

30:25.890 --> 30:26.850
at first,

30:27.400 --> 30:28.230
but always heard about

30:28.650 --> 30:30.320
Lu Chen in the 12th grade

30:30.760 --> 30:31.660
having a good look.

30:34.490 --> 30:35.280
And then?

30:38.030 --> 30:39.660
That's our business. Kids can't inquire about it.

30:42.920 --> 30:46.090
[Year 2020]

30:49.900 --> 30:54.420
