33:42.560 --> 33:43.400
I am no match for you.

33:50.690 --> 33:51.330
I'll use my left hand.

33:52.120 --> 33:53.950
The rule is who clears the table first, who wins.

33:57.940 --> 34:00.210
In this way, the chances of winning are high.

