Chen.

36:38.360 --> 36:39.040
Chen, are you leaving?

36:41.930 --> 36:42.920
Later I found out

36:43.870 --> 36:45.580
something happened to Lu Chen's family

36:44.270 --> 36:50.250
[Summer 2008]

36:46.360 --> 36:47.740
one day before the Gaokao.

36:48.920 --> 36:50.540
He didn't settle it until the next afternoon

36:51.250 --> 36:51.780
and missed

36:51.800 --> 36:53.200
the first exam in the morning.

36:54.650 --> 36:55.450
No one knew

36:55.450 --> 36:56.660
whether he was going to repeat his final year

36:57.250 --> 36:58.880
or work at the repair factory of his family.

37:00.330 --> 37:01.170
Since then,

37:01.890 --> 37:03.260
I never saw him again.

37:04.640 --> 37:05.240
Until...

37:06.040 --> 37:07.170
Sister-in-law, here.

37:07.620 --> 37:08.490
I'll treat you to pancakes.

37:17.650 --> 37:18.210
Take it easy.

37:27.570 --> 37:28.710
Here, the pancake is ready.

37:28.730 --> 37:29.780
Look how skinny my sister-in-law is.

37:30.840 --> 37:31.980
Add two eggs for me. Pick the big ones.

37:32.420 --> 37:32.910
Okay.

37:48.610 --> 37:49.810
Boss, a pancake, please.

37:50.090 --> 37:51.370
Okay, please wait a moment.

37:51.890 --> 37:53.260
Come on, handsome, your pancakes.

37:53.610 --> 37:54.160
Here.

37:54.930 --> 37:55.390
Thank you.

37:55.760 --> 37:56.500
You're welcome.

37:56.840 --> 37:57.720
My future bridesmaid.

38:06.060 --> 38:06.530
My bike.

38:23.970 --> 38:25.530
My brother didn't take the Gaokao that day

38:25.960 --> 38:27.200
because he applied for the police academy

38:27.230 --> 38:28.350
without telling his dad.

38:29.320 --> 38:31.040
His dad made a scene before the exam

38:31.410 --> 38:32.370
and locked him up in the garage

38:32.370 --> 38:33.730
for two days and three nights.

38:35.900 --> 38:37.420
The first exam was finished by then.

38:37.690 --> 38:38.280
He was released in secret

38:38.320 --> 38:39.430
by my aunt after that.

38:41.530 --> 38:42.770
But it was too late.

38:43.610 --> 38:44.510
Why?

38:45.090 --> 38:46.250
Even he applied for the police academy, so what?

38:48.460 --> 38:50.460
My aunt had divorced my uncle before.

38:51.530 --> 38:53.250
She married a cop after that.

38:55.070 --> 38:56.440
That cop was very nice.

38:56.690 --> 38:58.730
He treated my cousins well.

38:59.560 --> 39:01.950
But later he got sick and died.

39:04.080 --> 39:05.690
My aunt had no income.

39:05.970 --> 39:07.210
She couldn't afford to raise two children.

39:07.660 --> 39:09.630
So she remarried my uncle.

39:12.410 --> 39:13.610
Probably because of jealousy.

39:14.610 --> 39:15.770
I heard it from my mum.

39:17.210 --> 39:17.890
When my uncle

39:17.890 --> 39:19.520
knew my cousin had applied for the police academy,

39:19.690 --> 39:20.800
he went crazy.

39:22.690 --> 39:23.290
He must have recalled

39:23.290 --> 39:24.450
my aunt's second marriage.

39:27.050 --> 39:28.850
You can never ask

39:28.850 --> 39:29.850
my cousin about this.

39:31.610 --> 39:33.290
We don't talk much.

39:35.250 --> 39:35.740
Really?

39:37.090 --> 39:38.530
I thought you were close

39:38.670 --> 39:39.520
because of Meng Xiaoshan.

39:56.530 --> 39:58.500
Gui Xiao. I'll wait for you at the school gate.

39:58.780 --> 39:59.740
It's my brother's birthday today.

40:03.700 --> 40:05.080
Do I need to buy a gift?

40:05.750 --> 40:06.750
Come on.

40:07.200 --> 40:08.710
You bought plush toys

40:08.740 --> 40:10.350
for every student in our class on their birthdays.

40:10.410 --> 40:11.010
You've almost

40:11.010 --> 40:12.130
hollowed out the shop.

40:13.050 --> 40:14.410
Meng asked you to go empty-handed.

40:15.370 --> 40:16.210
Okay. Wait for me.

40:16.230 --> 40:16.870
I'll hand in the paper.

40:20.370 --> 40:22.210
He must be there on Haidong's birthday.

40:23.150 --> 40:28.230
[Lu Zheng Automobile Repair]

40:28.530 --> 40:29.980
This is the factory of Chen's family.

40:30.320 --> 40:31.880
But customers usually don't come here.

40:31.900 --> 40:33.100
They have to go to the storefront if they need the repairs.

40:36.250 --> 40:36.700
Chen.

41:12.730 --> 41:13.190
You're here.

41:13.210 --> 41:13.610
You're here.

41:13.970 --> 41:14.450
Sit here.

41:14.900 --> 41:15.340
Gui Xiao.

41:24.320 --> 41:25.130
Let me introduce them.

41:25.610 --> 41:27.090
These are my old classmates.

41:27.890 --> 41:29.290
This is Meng Xiaoshan's sister.

41:29.320 --> 41:29.950
Her name is Gui Xiao.

41:30.630 --> 41:31.640
This is my younger brother, Hai Jianfeng.

41:32.100 --> 41:32.740
They are our own people.

41:34.770 --> 41:35.930
Lu Chen's room is too cold.

41:35.930 --> 41:36.530
Put it on.

41:39.450 --> 41:40.640
You guys are still in high school.

41:40.730 --> 41:41.530
You can't drink.

41:42.010 --> 41:42.880
